snippet.title: AH & her team start using The CHEWBACCA DEFENSE!! (Depp, Amber, South Park)
snippet.description:
AH & her team start using The CHEWBACCA DEFENSE!! (Depp, Amber, South Park)

Yes, you read that correctly. AH and her team are using the Chewbacca defense from an episode of South Park. Overloading people with evidence that doesn't even need to be there. 

Asking for every tiny detail overloads people's minds and they cannot think straight.
